I remember, correct me if I'm wrong, lime green underwear.

72
00:03:09,310 --> 00:03:10,500
更多的是薄荷绿 
More of a minty green.

73
00:03:10,500 --> 00:03:11,450
哦 我明白了
Oh, I see.

74
00:03:11,450 --> 00:03:13,830
但是我确实记得你把我喝趴下了
I do remember you drinking me under the table, though..

75
00:03:15,610 --> 00:03:17,480
这是干嘛 早晨例会?
 What's this, an early briefing?

76
00:03:17,680 --> 00:03:20,100
约翰 你来了 好极了
John, there you are, good.

77
00:03:21,030 --> 00:03:22,750
这位是马库斯・杰克斯 
This is Marcus Jakes,

78
00:03:22,750 --> 00:03:23,930
- 是个卧底 - 没错
- he's a U.C. - Right.

79
00:03:23,970 --> 00:03:26,060
