Hey. John Moreland, in the flesh.

80
00:03:26,080 --> 00:03:28,550
- 哥们 听过你很多事情 - 你好
- The stories I hear about you, brother. - How you doing?

81
00:03:28,570 --> 00:03:30,940
杰克斯和我一起加入警队 一个警局
Jakes and I were in uniform together. Same division.

82
00:03:30,960 --> 00:03:32,270
世界真小啊
Small world.

83
00:03:32,280 --> 00:03:33,660
我过去经常逗她开心
I used to make her laugh so hard

84
00:03:33,670 --> 00:03:35,520
弄得她连咖啡都呛到鼻子里
 that coffee would shoot out her nose.

85
00:03:35,710 --> 00:03:37,090
