87
00:03:41,280 --> 00:03:43,610
- 是啊 - 是的
- Right. - Yeah.

88
00:03:46,540 --> 00:03:49,160
阿里・雷曼 专门收保护费
Ali Raman, runs a protection racket.

89
00:03:49,160 --> 00:03:51,260
非法赌博 严刑 谋杀
Illegal gambling, torture, murder.

90
00:03:51,280 --> 00:03:53,310
他有个地下搏击场 生意相当火爆
He's got an underground fight club, it's pretty intense.

91
00:03:53,330 --> 00:03:55,530
是的 我听说过这家伙 他就是个疯子
Yeah, I've heard of this guy, he's a borderline psychopath.

92
00:03:55,570 --> 00:03:57,040
杰克斯打入内部卧底
Jakes has been deep undercover.

93
00:03:57,060 --> 00:03:58,400
- 八个月 - 厉害啊
- Eight months. - Cool.

94
00:03:58,430 --> 00:04:01,030
我已经在他的组织做到了副手
My path into Raman's operation has been through his lieutenant.

95
00:04:01,070 --> 00:04:02,540
一个叫瑞克・加齐的
A guy named Ric Gazi.

96
00:04:03,020 --> 00:04:06,080
- 哦 看啊 - 是魔术
- Oh. Look at that. - It's magic.

97
00:04:07,180 --> 00:04:09,130
好吧 我卧底在加齐的组织 
Ok, I'm in deep with Gazi...

98
00:04:09,130 --> 00:04:10,480
一路从他的手下做起
Worked my way onto his crew.

99
00:04:10,600 --> 00:04:12,190
你一直在做什么?
 And you've been doing what?

100
00:04:13,030 --> 00:04:14,790
你知道的 收收钱 
You know, collections.

101
00:04:14,790 --> 00:04:16,930
砸砸店铺 吓吓人什么的
Trashing stores, intimidating folks, that kind of thing.

102
00:04:16,960 --> 00:04:18,340
我现在就能逮捕加齐 
I could arrest Gazi right now,

103
00:04:18,350 --> 00:04:19,590
但是他不是我的重点
but he is not my focus.

104
00:04:19,610 --> 00:04:20,970
我想要的是这个人 
I want this guy.

105
00:04:20,970 --> 00:04:22,480
我想抓雷曼 幕后老大
I want Raman, I want the boss.

106
00:04:22,510 --> 00:04:24,120
重案组要求我们协助 
Major Crimes is asking us to help out.

107
00:04:24,120 --> 00:04:25,860
为什么 你的管理员呢?
Why, where's your handler?

108
00:04:26,510 --> 00:04:28,590
他的管理员是是斯图・克劳德 他现在不在了
The handler was Stu Crowder, he's out of the picture.

109
00:04:28,710 --> 00:04:30,370
不在了 这是什么意思?
Out of the picture, what does that suppose to mean?

110
00:04:30,370 --> 00:04:31,570
他怎么了?
What happened to him?

111
00:04:31,690 --> 00:04:33,470
哦 威士忌
Uh, whiskey...

112
00:04:33,590 --> 00:04:36,190
先是威士忌 再是杜松子酒 如果有的话
...happened to him. Followed by gin, followed by paint thinner,

113
00:04:36,220 --> 00:04:37,540
油漆稀释剂
if that's what he had around.

114
00:04:38,190 --> 00:04:39,660
过了一阵子 他就不来找我了
After a while he just stopped checking in.

115
00:04:39,700 --> 00:04:41,380
我要求全面监控还有支援 
I'd called for surveillance, and backup,

116
00:04:41,380 --> 00:04:42,360
结果什么都没有
I get nothing.

117
00:04:42,380 --> 00:04:43,870
我全靠我自己
I was completely on my own.

118
00:04:45,610 --> 00:04:48,850
杰克斯先生 我们能为你做什么?
So, what can we do for you, Mr. Jakes?

119
00:04:49,720 --> 00:04:52,420
我的加齐宝贝 野心勃勃
My boy Gazi, he's got ambitions.

120
00:04:52,450 --> 00:04:54,980
他打算做掉雷曼 计划找杀手来做
He's wants to take out Raman. He's planning a hit.

121
00:04:55,280 --> 00:04:56,570
我们不能坐视不理
We can't let that happen.

122
00:04:56,600 --> 00:04:58,680
- 所以我们要先下手为强 - 嗯
- So we're going to get in front of it. - Mh-hmm...

123
00:04:58,690 --> 00:05:01,620
你会是我的老朋友 杀手约翰
You are going to be my old friend John the hit-man.

124
00:05:02,080 --> 00:05:03,680
我会把你介绍给加齐
I'm going to introduce you to Gazi.

125
00:05:03,710 --> 00:05:06,240
你会去见他 和他聊聊 和他达成协议
You're gonna meet him, you're gonna talk to him, you're gonna take the contract.

126
00:05:06,250 --> 00:05:07,680
然后我就可以抓他了  
And then we pick him up.

127
00:05:07,680 --> 00:05:08,890
意图谋杀 罪名不小
Conspiracy to murder, that's big.

128
00:05:08,900 --> 00:05:10,340
是的 我不想让他耽误我的案子
Yeah, I need him out of the way.

129
00:05:10,340 --> 00:05:11,370
我要抓的是他的老板
 I need a clear shot at his boss.

130
00:05:11,400 --> 00:05:13,140
我想雷曼进监狱 不是要他死
I want Raman in prison, not dead.

131
00:05:13,200 --> 00:05:14,800
好了 听着 我们第一步
Alright, listen up. Our first step...

132
00:05:14,830 --> 00:05:16,160
稍等一下
 Just wait a second.

133
00:05:16,200 --> 00:05:17,990
你怎么知道这次暗杀是他策划的?
How do you know about this hit he's got planned?

134
00:05:17,990 --> 00:05:19,360
他告诉我的
He told me.

135
00:05:19,620 --> 00:05:21,970
所以你没有建议他这样做
So you didn't offer?

136
00:05:22,520 --> 00:05:24,090
没有 当然没有
No, of course not.

137
00:05:24,090 --> 00:05:25,400
你想说什么?
What's your point?

138
00:05:25,600 --> 00:05:27,100
我想说 我想知道我到底
My point is, is just I want to know

139
00:05:27,100 --> 00:05:28,460
走进的是个什么样的局
 what I'm walking myself into here.

140
00:05:28,520 --> 00:05:30,080
要确保这次会面没有问题
Make sure this meet is clean.

141
00:05:30,200 --> 00:05:32,780
放松 我知道自己在做什么
Relax. I know what I'm doing.

142
00:05:32,870 --> 00:05:34,550
这次行动没问题
The job is solid.

143
00:05:37,800 --> 00:05:39,690
