You'll be our eyes in there.

146
00:05:44,250 --> 00:05:46,020
我需要给你装上监听装置
I'm going to have to wire you.

147
00:05:46,290 --> 00:05:49,200
看你的衣服 我只能把东西安在你的前胸上了
With what you're wearing, I'm gonna have to do your chest.

