00:06:05,730 --> 00:06:07,230
没什么
Nothing.

152
00:06:08,180 --> 00:06:09,380
过来
Come here.

153
00:06:14,730 --> 00:06:17,160
加齐会在他的俱乐部 那是他在那做生意
 Gazi will be at the club, that's where he does business.

154
00:06:17,180 --> 00:06:19,720
杰克斯 你带约翰进去 把他介绍给加齐
Jakes, you're gonna walk John inside, introduce him.

155
00:06:19,720 --> 00:06:21,140
