We'll be recording everything.

156
00:06:21,170 --> 00:06:24,170
一旦加齐让约翰达成协议 我们就抓到他了
As soon as Gazi offers John the contract, we got him.

157
00:06:32,920 --> 00:06:34,470
好的 他们刚进来
Alright, they just came in.

158
00:06:34,700 --> 00:06:36,790
杰西 一定要盯住他们
Jesse, make sure you keep them in sight.

159
00:06:36,810 --> 00:06:37,720
收到
Copy that.

