Chewy says he's sorry, won't be late again.

184
00:07:37,720 --> 00:07:39,800
别说我没给你钱
Don't say I never gave you nothing.

185
00:07:42,850 --> 00:07:45,010
哦 这位是我朋友 就是那个人
Oh, this is my friend. This is the guy.

186
00:07:45,580 --> 00:07:47,070
